{"tid":92043,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"四年感情，完了","createTime":"2017-01-23T09:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T15:15:53.000Z","uid":78587,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2d3f1780edaefb7fdf466df285412b7adb6ae5","tid":92043,"uid":78587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:49:53.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左四年<br />\n原本簡唔鐘有嗌交<br />\n覺得永遠都會原諒<br />\n但今次....<br />\n<br />\n識左男朋友半年𣊬速一齊左<br />\nKeep 到好好感情<br />\n其他人都覺得好恩愛<br />\n個個人都問幾時結婚<br />\n但因為開始大個<br />\n逐漸知道要為自己負責<br />\n男朋友開始賺錢<br />\n我就繼續努力讀書<br />\n直到開始第一次賭<br />\n有贏有輸<br />\n但最後梗係輸到仆直<br />\n<br />\n男朋友依家覺得失去生活保障<br />\n想自己一個人努力<br />\n想我改變下<br />\n有機會會再一齊<br />\n<br />\n今次竟然好和平咁分手<br />\n和平到我覺得好恐怖<br />\n可能之前未試過係咁<br />\n大家用左幾日去適應分手<br />\n依幾日都唔知自己做過咩黎<br />\n我知道佢唔係有新女(可以好肯定)<br />\n我都知道佢講既都係真<br />\n好不知所措<br />\n怕自己改變到男朋友都冇機會再愛自己<br />\n希望大家個緣份仲係到....<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a455d94792d1c8026e06708dd4d8beb0b3ce9370","tid":92043,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:52:26.000Z","msg":"賭 抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f6f1cf305970e0a81de0da58efb84f63faf03e","tid":92043,"uid":78587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"男朋友賭<br />\n我都想阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8758aba79f8ca5b041979e75524e85e774c36607","tid":92043,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:55:54.000Z","msg":"男人賭就話抵死姐<br />\n女人都走去賭 無藥救架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戒左賭先再諗有無得一齊返啦<br />\n賭到嚇走人 你應該都有排先戒得甩"},{"pid":"4c841b9608d0e4d9495791a56743ddb795c79c85","tid":92043,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:56:30.000Z","msg":"唔趁早分手唔通等你爭落一身債要佢孭上身先嚟分呀?<br />\n錢都未識賺就學人爛賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c28607ccd5e6e357f51a0324b0be85c66c294c","tid":92043,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男朋友賭<br />\n我都想阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一係你同佢傾 一係你用將來威逼 <br />\n一係你由佢賭到傾家蕩產都可能有得救"},{"pid":"bade1b9af23085056d20c345041167f83e6d6a2a","tid":92043,"uid":78587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:57:50.000Z","msg":"係男朋友賭啊...."},{"pid":"66521fad3c042061bf7107081e1faf1e6dc749c9","tid":92043,"uid":218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男朋友賭<br />\n我都想阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1999<br />\n爛賭嘅人要嚟都冇用 遲早累埋你"},{"pid":"dfe9167a70cdbc88c54c5bcf78068ffd08c87120","tid":92043,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係男朋友賭啊....</blockquote><br />\n唔賭既男人要黎都無撚用<br />\n我係絲都係咁話"},{"pid":"f826facddf58aa4ea2d98dab7972160b6d5ba7a0","tid":92043,"uid":78587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男朋友賭<br />\n我都想阻止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一係你同佢傾 一係你用將來威逼 <br />\n一係你由佢賭到傾家蕩產都可能有得救</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家見面都冇<br />\n不過佢都已經賭到冇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f77d83dc3df50e01991b42a3e26f5930c4e9d986","tid":92043,"uid":78587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:02:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係男朋友賭啊....</blockquote><br />\n唔賭既男人要黎都無撚用<br />\n我係絲都係咁話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都想放得底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3063e6370b2820edc37e4bb82a138cd71250688","tid":92043,"uid":59059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"你當俾機會佢改lor<br />\n為佢又好為自己都好<br />\n<br />\n自己果邊就慢慢冷靜下，搵下朋友仔出街食飯<br />\n唔好諗咁多啦"},{"pid":"49c13e843a46c3a436c59424f4859d9e42dfcdbc","tid":92043,"uid":75359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"讀咩書讀到中文都表達成咁"},{"pid":"83bf51b26b28d63d794eb2219cc9e23a463d1f5a","tid":92043,"uid":78587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:09:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你當俾機會佢改lor<br />\n為佢又好為自己都好<br />\n<br />\n自己果邊就慢慢冷靜下，搵下朋友仔出街食飯<br />\n唔好諗咁多啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能我太重視<br />\n依家每日都好似呆下呆下<br />\n集中唔到諗野<br />\n<br />\n但係咪真係有得挽回...."},{"pid":"53ec695689615a3951b3d1e5d13d4e622188d541","tid":92043,"uid":59059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你當俾機會佢改lor<br />\n為佢又好為自己都好<br />\n<br />\n自己果邊就慢慢冷靜下，搵下朋友仔出街食飯<br />\n唔好諗咁多啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能我太重視<br />\n依家每日都好似呆下呆下<br />\n集中唔到諗野<br />\n<br />\n但係咪真係有得挽回....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講左和平分手<br />\n就真係，真係，真係要向前看<br />\n唔好諗挽回喇<br />\n<br />\n再者，如果佢真係唔再賭，都要睇大家果時仲係咪愛對方<br />\n<br />\n4年感情係會唔惜得<br />\n但真係要放手，集中唔到諗野正常<br />\n喊都正常<br />\n<br />\n但要remind自己要有喊完既一日，從新開始"},{"pid":"38f5ce420ce4bdbb67c44ca40a3599031bb8f0da","tid":92043,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:16:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係男朋友賭啊....</blockquote><br />\n中文咁廢就咪上連登<br />\n讀下中學先啦"},{"pid":"7a2525de6e4ff8f804be54d7e93a89908c951a7a","tid":92043,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:18:50.000Z","msg":"199999999999999<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n齋睇你篇野都可以搞到大家錯晒邊個賭"},{"pid":"88443ca55ddc8e9d8ee4b9c5446cabdeebfe4027","tid":92043,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"其實你都無厭棄佢<br />\n佢反而同你分手<br />\n而唔係同你一齊諗解決方法<br />\n呢d臉皮咁薄既廢物<br />\n只可共富貴 不可共患難<br />\n就算鳩數吧啦"},{"pid":"4bb34172e2454eac40406dd9f05909a3d2cf084f","tid":92043,"uid":78587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你都無厭棄佢<br />\n佢反而同你分手<br />\n而唔係同你一齊諗解決方法<br />\n呢d臉皮咁薄既廢物<br />\n只可共富貴 不可共患難<br />\n就算鳩數吧啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢覺得咁樣對我最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家都係咁喊<br />\n兩邊都好唔捨得"},{"pid":"1b158532ae6dccb3e04f3f41d3311c66ba024bb8","tid":92043,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:22:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你都無厭棄佢<br />\n佢反而同你分手<br />\n而唔係同你一齊諗解決方法<br />\n呢d臉皮咁薄既廢物<br />\n只可共富貴 不可共患難<br />\n就算鳩數吧啦</blockquote><br />\n首先無富貴過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41d997b07d904850526e786861b969bbf0d86a5","tid":92043,"uid":75726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"通常都唔會再有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我同條女一齊左三年幾 都和平分手 雖然話日後再想一齊返 但都知無咩可能"},{"pid":"5ab91efc704c1e0a7b8de2e8d5a355c6dd608560","tid":92043,"uid":36479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀咩書讀到中文都表達成咁</blockquote><br />\nagree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2e9d2b7740cf98019edd2fe95c7d1690910b91","tid":92043,"uid":78785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:26:31.000Z","msg":"大家都可能攰啦<br />\n<br />\n始終生活太辛苦啦"},{"pid":"e42b1c0ec41e59b2151af547e730139f00bff9a5","tid":92043,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"條女1999 我係仔都走"},{"pid":"b02a8134edd32a2a2f74330698c4232436eab4dd","tid":92043,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"講野講到岩，視你以後無仔兼死全族"}]}